snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutants in Manhattan
snippet.description:
Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles™: Mutants in Manhattan
• 4-player online co-op mode!
• Fight fan-favorite enemies like Bebop and Rocksteady! 
• PlatinumGames’ signature fast-paced combat!
